item.title: Castlewars Portals not teleporting
item.dc:creator: @genoarch genoarch
item.description:
@genoarch wrote:

see the only thing is ive edited this source a TON so its pretty much not even close to the same as combattscape, ive added the Castlewars to the game, ive searched up the portal ids and case numbers and junk and removed all the ones that do not pertain ot castlewars, which is all of them since the castlewars class handles all the cases and object ids for castlewars, but still it will NOT teleport me idk why?

EDIT: I figured out the Problem, the integer defined when teleporting you to position multiplayed by 3 could not be determined so it wouldnt teleport me, instead of teleporting me to a coord and then multiplying it by 3 to make it random i just made it send me to a location not random. Directly to the Coords
